original_title: Prime Cut Video Magazine Vol. 6 - Reunion Of The Stars
overview: Brett Mycles, Tyler Stone, Dante and Derec Hardman re-unite in a once-in-a-lifetime get-together that eclipses all previous "Prime Cut" videos. With interviews, shower scenes and a photo shoot, the viewer gets a first-hand look into the private lives, experiences and bodies of these Jet Set Exclusives. A magnificent final chapter to this series!!!
title: Prime Cut Video Magazine Vol. 6 - Reunion Of The Stars
